        <abstract> 
<p>Praises <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Reports on Fritz Müller’s observations of cross- and self-fertilisation. HM will cultivate the two forms [i.e., mainly self-fertilised and mainly cross-fertilised] in the way CD has described.</p> 
<p>He continues his observation of wild flowers. Encloses drawing of <hi rend="italic">Viola tricolor</hi> with notes on its self-fertility.</p> 
        </abstract>
